<HL>
   Senate Adopts $54 Billion Farm Bill,
   Renewing Thrust of Agriculture Policy
   ----
   By Bruce Ingersoll
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/30/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
